snippet.title: MiniDoom 2 Launch Trailer
snippet.description:
You can download and play MiniDoom 2 for free at our site! http://calavera.studio/minidoom2/

The trailer for our secund indi game! A fan game that pays homage to the Doom franchise by reimagining it as a 2d retro platformer!

Game design and programing: Felipe Porcel
https://www.facebook.com/felipe.porcel/

Graphics and animation: Juan Carlos Porcel
https://twitter.com/jcporcel

Music and SFX: Manuel Soruco
https://www.facebook.com/JoseManuelSoruco
